{"tid":2013794,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警甴：100萬 THX","createTime":"2020-05-12T14:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T16:53:58.000Z","uid":216992,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab31804ecfbf12601eba92a246d9b9044c7b5ff","tid":2013794,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:06:03.000Z","msg":"【 感謝 &bull; 100萬次的支持】<br />\n<br />\n自去年十月推出「反暴力報料熱線」以來，警方共收到超過100萬條報料訊息，當中包括非法集結、縱火、行劫、傷人及爆炸品等相關情報。市民透過熱線提供線索，以行動表明和暴力「割蓆」的決心。<br />\n<br />\n警方衷心感謝市民報料，情報往往都是破案的關鍵。警方深信不久將來，社會必能重回正軌，重新出發。<br />\n<br />\n請大家繼續力撐「反暴力報料熱線」，協助警方將暴徒繩之於法！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#100萬THX</span><br />\n#反暴力<br />\n#百萬人一條心<br />\n#平台總有一個喺你手機<br />\n#電子化割蓆"},{"pid":"4bc4fd41241e0aa4e890e3fa3350196b7d3a8e4c","tid":2013794,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKteuDo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKteuDo.jpg&h=8232dabe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5R41T44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5R41T44.jpg&h=2f736ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00p1T45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00p1T45.jpg&h=3ab0e29e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"011949f43cb01e03817725b36214f89ced3a5da3","tid":2013794,"uid":216992,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上次30萬like數thx 7咗<br />\n而家再黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabeed597f59f485a117e9b1f7c66a63596a408f","tid":2013794,"uid":216992,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:08:01.000Z","msg":"拎數字黎打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149e0f78b5811227e09c40a